        { "id": "s4-col2-i3", "type": "text", "content": "›  Deposit asset / liability FCY split", "x": 3.62, "y": 4.9, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "F87171", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col2-i4", "type": "text", "content": "›  Period-end remeasurement attribution by item", "x": 3.62, "y": 5.66, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "F87171", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 6.7, "y": 2.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 4.9, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 6.7, "y": 2.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "FCD34D", "color": "FCD34D" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-title", "type": "text", "content": "Why This Matters for NOP", "x": 6.82, "y": 2.12, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.44, "style": { "fontSize": 10.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-i0", "type": "text", "content": "›  NOP cannot be computed without B/S decomposition", "x": 6.82, "y": 2.62, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-i1", "type": "text", "content": "›  Hedge ratio is calculated on incomplete exposure", "x": 6.82, "y": 3.38, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-i2", "type": "text", "content": "›  Over- or under-hedging is structurally possible", "x": 6.82, "y": 4.14, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-i3", "type": "text", "content": "›  GAAP remeasurement surprise cannot be forecast", "x": 6.82, "y": 4.9, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-col3-i4", "type": "text", "content": "›  Currency risk dashboard shows partial picture only", "x": 6.82, "y": 5.66, "w": 2.76, "h": 0.68, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s4-warning-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 7.0, "w": 9.4, "h": 0.38, "style": { "bg": "7F1D1D", "color": "7F1D1D" } },
        { "id": "s4-warning", "type": "text", "content": "⚠  Without B/S decomposition in NetSuite, NOP is a partial estimate — not a risk-management-grade number.", "x": 0.45, "y": 7.0, "w": 9.1, "h": 0.38, "style": { "fontSize": 10.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-5",
      "bg": "0D1B2A",
      "elements": [
        { "id": "s5-title", "type": "text", "content": "No Reconciliation Bridge — The Gap Compounds Over Time", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.18, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.54, "style": { "fontSize": 26, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-title-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.72, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s5-sub", "type": "text", "content": "Without a recon process, the delta between GAAP P&L and Management P&L is never explained or closed", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.8, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.3, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "color": "64748B", "italic": true, "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-recon-label", "type": "text", "content": "WHAT A RECONCILIATION BRIDGE REQUIRES:", "x": 0.4, "y": 1.1, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.3, "style": { "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "color": "64748B", "charSpacing": 2, "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-step1", "type": "chip", "content": "Management\nP&L", "x": 0.3, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.5, "h": 0.82, "style": { "bg": "60A5FA", "color": "FFFFFF", "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s5-step2", "type": "chip", "content": "±  Gross vs Net\nDerivative Presentation", "x": 2.02, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.72, "h": 0.82, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "FFFFFF", "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s5-step3", "type": "chip", "content": "±  Accrual-to-Pricing\nTiming Window", "x": 3.96, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.52, "h": 0.82, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "FFFFFF", "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s5-step4", "type": "chip", "content": "±  Option Time\nValue (decay)", "x": 5.7, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.52, "h": 0.82, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "FFFFFF", "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s5-step5", "type": "chip", "content": "±  Rate Source\nDifference", "x": 7.44, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.42, "h": 0.82, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "FFFFFF", "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s5-divider", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.4, "y": 2.55, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s5-blockers-label", "type": "text", "content": "WHY THIS BRIDGE CANNOT BE BUILT TODAY:", "x": 0.4, "y": 2.62, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.3, "style": { "fontSize": 9, "bold": true, "color": "F87171", "charSpacing": 2, "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b1-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b1-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s5-b1-title", "type": "text", "content": "01  NOP Not Available from NetSuite", "x": 0.4, "y": 3.12, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b1-body", "type": "text", "content": "NetSuite does not produce a currency-level net open position report. FCY assets and liabilities are not decomposed by currency in any standard report — the exposure baseline is missing.", "x": 0.4, "y": 3.52, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b2-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 3.53, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b2-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 3.53, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s5-b2-title", "type": "text", "content": "02  No Item-Level Remeasurement Attribution", "x": 3.63, "y": 3.12, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b2-body", "type": "text", "content": "ASC 830 remeasurement is posted as a single line 'FX Gain/Loss' in the P&L. There is no breakdown by asset/liability type, currency, or transaction — making attribution to management trades impossible.", "x": 3.63, "y": 3.52, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b3-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 6.76, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b3-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 6.76, "y": 3.05, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "FCD34D", "color": "FCD34D" } },
        { "id": "s5-b3-title", "type": "text", "content": "03  Derivative Presentation Mismatch", "x": 6.86, "y": 3.12, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b3-body", "type": "text", "content": "Management records derivatives net (offset against hedged position). GAAP requires gross fair value. Without mapping each derivative to its management counterpart, the gross/net reconciliation cannot be computed.", "x": 6.86, "y": 3.52, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b4-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b4-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "FCD34D", "color": "FCD34D" } },
        { "id": "s5-b4-title", "type": "text", "content": "04  Accrual-to-Pricing Timing Gap Not Tracked", "x": 0.4, "y": 5.22, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b4-body", "type": "text", "content": "GAAP accrues the invoice before the FX rate is set. Management captures it only at pricing date. Accrued-but-unpriced invoices sit on the GAAP B/S with FX exposure the risk desk cannot yet see.", "x": 0.4, "y": 5.62, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b5-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 3.53, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b5-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 3.53, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "A78BFA", "color": "A78BFA" } },
        { "id": "s5-b5-title", "type": "text", "content": "05  Intercompany & Deposit Balances Excluded", "x": 3.63, "y": 5.22, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b5-body", "type": "text", "content": "FCY intercompany balances and deposit liabilities are fully monetary under ASC 830 and remeasured every period. They do not appear in the management risk framework at all — creating a systematically growing blind spot.", "x": 3.63, "y": 5.62, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b6-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 6.76, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 1.96, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s5-b6-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 6.76, "y": 5.15, "w": 3.0, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "A78BFA", "color": "A78BFA" } },
        { "id": "s5-b6-title", "type": "text", "content": "06  Option Time Value Treated Differently", "x": 6.86, "y": 5.22, "w": 2.8, "h": 0.34, "style": { "fontSize": 9.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s5-b6-body", "type": "text", "content": "GAAP records full option premium as an asset; time value decay hits I/S as expense. Management treats the premium as a hedge cost embedded in the position. The divergence accumulates across all option trades.", "x": 6.86, "y": 5.62, "w": 2.78, "h": 1.38, "style": { "fontSize": 8.5, "color": "CBD5E1", "align": "left" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-6",
      "bg": "0D1B2A",
      "elements": [
        { "id": "s6-title", "type": "text", "content": "What We Cannot Do — The Consequence Cascade", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.18, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.54, "style": { "fontSize": 26, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-title-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.72, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.04, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s6-sub", "type": "text", "content": "One root cause. Twelve capabilities we do not have today.", "x": 0.4, "y": 0.8, "w": 9.2, "h": 0.3, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "color": "64748B", "italic": true, "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-root-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 1.1, "w": 9.4, "h": 0.56, "style": { "bg": "7F1D1D", "color": "7F1D1D" } },
        { "id": "s6-root-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 1.1, "w": 9.4, "h": 0.05, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s6-root-text", "type": "text", "content": "ROOT CAUSE  ·  FX management captures trade flows only — every FCY item posted to the balance sheet is invisible to the risk framework", "x": 0.46, "y": 1.1, "w": 9.1, "h": 0.56, "style": { "fontSize": 11, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-hdr-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.4, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "162C44" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-hdr-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.05, "style": { "bg": "F87171", "color": "F87171" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-hdr", "type": "text", "content": "EXPOSURE", "x": 0.4, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.0, "h": 0.4, "style": { "fontSize": 10, "bold": true, "color": "F87171", "align": "left", "charSpacing": 1.5 } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-r0", "type": "rect", "content": "NOP cannot be computed", "x": 0.3, "y": 2.36, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.62, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236", "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color2": "FFFFFF", "align": "center" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-t0", "type": "text", "content": "NOP cannot be computed", "x": 0.46, "y": 2.36, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-r1", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 3.08, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.62, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "162C44" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-t1", "type": "text", "content": "No real-time exposure view", "x": 0.46, "y": 3.08, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-r2", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 0.3, "y": 3.8, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.62, "style": { "bg": "112236", "color": "112236" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat1-t2", "type": "text", "content": "Accrued-not-yet-priced invoices missed", "x": 0.46, "y": 3.8, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-hdr-bg", "type": "rect", "content": "", "x": 2.68, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.4, "style": { "bg": "162C44", "color": "162C44" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-hdr-bar", "type": "bar", "content": "", "x": 2.68, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.18, "h": 0.05, "style": { "bg": "FCD34D", "color": "FCD34D" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-hdr", "type": "text", "content": "P&L INTEGRITY", "x": 2.78, "y": 1.88, "w": 2.0, "h": 0.4, "style": { "fontSize": 10, "bold": true, "color": "FCD34D", "align": "left", "charSpacing": 1.5 } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-t0", "type": "text", "content": "P&L recon bridge impossible", "x": 2.84, "y": 2.36, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-t1", "type": "text", "content": "FX surprises at period close", "x": 2.84, "y": 3.08, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
        { "id": "s6-cat2-t2", "type": "text", "content": "Hedge effectiveness unknown", "x": 2.84, "y": 3.8, "w": 1.96, "h": 0.62, "style": { "fontSize": 11.5, "bold": true, "color": "FFFFFF", "align": "left" } },
